<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="subtle-adj">subtle <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sʌtl/    美 /'sʌtl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>难以察觉的；微妙的；精巧的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>subtle differences / changes 
细微的差异/变化</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>subtle flavours / smells</strong>
淡淡的味道/气味</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a subtle device 
精巧的设计</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Can you tell the <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ difference between the words “require” and “request”? I sometimes get puzzled by their meanings.  （2012 湖北）<br />
A.dramatic<br />
B.regional<br />
C.apparent<br />
D.subtle  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. D  </p></div>